        &lt;h1 class="page-title"&gt;WebPage Syntax Demo&lt;/h1&gt;
        &lt;p class="subtitle"&gt;Case-insensitive!&lt;/p&gt;
        ...
    &lt;/div&gt;
&#125;</code></pre>
        </section>

        <section class="demo-section">
